BIOMES

Pasta: data/biomes
Cada arquivo JSON segue o modelo BiomeDef.

Campos:
- id: string
- name: string
- description: string
- monsterTagWeights: { tag: weight }
- summonChanceBonusPct: number
- healingMultiplier: number
- eventRoomChanceBonusPct: int
- npcEventBonusPct: int

Exemplo:
{
  "id": "wilds",
  "name": "Selvagem",
  "monsterTagWeights": { "beast": 1.2 },
  "summonChanceBonusPct": 5.0,
  "healingMultiplier": 1.0,
  "eventRoomChanceBonusPct": 0,
  "npcEventBonusPct": 0
}
